<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
      <%= @form.t([@form.ineligibility_reason, "heading"]) %>
    </h1>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      Based on our records, the nursery you selected is not currently eligible for the early years teacher recognition payment.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      To be eligible, you must teach at an early years group-based setting that offers the early years entitlements.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      If you think this is a mistake, check you’ve selected the correct nursery. If the problem continues, contact <%= govuk_mail_to t("early_years_teachers_financial_incentive_payments.support_email_address") %>.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      <%= govuk_link_to(
        "What do you think of this service?",
        "https://TBC"
      ) %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
